{{Main article|氧的同位素}}
[[File:Evolved_star_fusion_shells.svg|thumb]]
自然界中的氧元素由<chem>^16O</chem>、<chem>^17O</chem>及<chem>^18O</chem>三種穩定[[同位素|同位素]]組成，其中<chem>^16O</chem>的[[豐度|豐度]]最高（99.762%）。<ref name="EnvChem-Iso">{{cite web|url=http://environmentalchemistry.com/yogi/periodic/O-pg2.html|title=Oxygen Nuclides / Isotopes|publisher=EnvironmentalChemistry.com|accessdate=2007-12-17|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818214039/https://environmentalchemistry.com/yogi/periodic/O-pg2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

大部分<chem>^16O</chem>是在大質量[[恆星|恆星]][[3氦過程|氦聚變]]過程晚期[[核合成|合成]]，也有一部分源於[[氖燃燒過程|氖燃燒過程]]。<ref name="Meyer2005">{{cite conference|first=B. S.|last=Meyer|title=Nucleosynthesis and Galactic Chemical Evolution of the Isotopes of Oxygen|conference=Workgroup on Oxygen in the Earliest Solar System|date=REG9EX 19–21, 2005|location=Gatlinburg, Tennessee|url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/ess2005/pdf/9022.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2007-01-22|work=Proceedings of the NASA Cosmochemistry Program and the Lunar and Planetary Institute|conferenceurl=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/ess2005/|id=9022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101229194925/http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/ess2005/pdf/9022.pdf|archive-date=2010-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><chem>^17O</chem>主要是在[[碳氮氧循環|碳氮氧循環]]中從氫至氦的聚變過程中產生，因此分佈在恆星內部的氫聚變區域。<ref name="Meyer2005"/>[[氮的同位素|<sup>14</sup>N]]在捕獲一個[[氦的同位素|<sup>4</sup>He]]原子核後變為<chem>^18O</chem>，因此<chem>^18O</chem>分佈在大質量恆星的氦區域。<ref name="Meyer2005"/>

在穩定同位素以外，氧還有14種[[放射性同位素|放射性同位素]]。最穩定的為<chem>^15O</chem>和<chem>^14O</chem>，[[半衰期|半衰期]]分別為122.24秒和70.606秒。<ref name="EnvChem-Iso"/>其餘的放射性同位素半衰期都在27秒以內，大部分甚至低於83毫秒。<ref name="EnvChem-Iso"/>質量低於<chem>^16O</chem>的同位素的最常見衰變模式為[[正電子發射|β<sup>+</sup>]]，<ref name="NUDAT-13O">{{cite web|url=http://www.nndc.bnl.gov/nudat2/decaysearchdirect.jsp?nuc=13O&unc=nds|title=NUDAT 13O|accessdate=2009-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080924161826/http://www.nndc.bnl.gov/nudat2/decaysearchdirect.jsp?nuc=13O&unc=nds|archive-date=2008-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NUDAT-14O">{{cite web|url=http://www.nndc.bnl.gov/nudat2/decaysearchdirect.jsp?nuc=14O&unc=nds|title=NUDAT 14O|accessdate=2009-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080924151512/http://www.nndc.bnl.gov/nudat2/decaysearchdirect.jsp?nuc=14O&unc=nds|archive-date=2008-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NUDAT-15O">{{cite web|url=http://www.nndc.bnl.gov/nudat2/decaysearchdirect.jsp?nuc=15O&unc=nds|title=NUDAT 15O|accessdate=2009-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721052246/http://www.nndc.bnl.gov/nudat2/decaysearchdirect.jsp?nuc=15O&unc=nds|archive-date=2011-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>產物為[[氮|氮]]；質量高於<chem>^18O</chem>的同位素則主要進行<math>\beta^-</math>衰變，產物為[[氟|氟]]。<ref name="EnvChem-Iso"/>

